tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE social_media_engagement_metrics (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_name VARCHAR(255),
    engagement_score INT,
    post_likes INT,
    post_comments INT
)

CREATE TABLE social_media_engagement_metrics (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT,
    post_id INT,
    likes INT,
    comments INT,
    shares INT
)

CREATE TABLE influencers (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255),
    followers INT,
    engagement_rate FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE posts (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    post_text TEXT,
    post_date TIMESTAMP,
    influencer_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE posts (
    post_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT,
   post_content STRING,
    likes INT,
    comments INT
);

CREATE TABLE analytics (
    analytics_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    post_id INT,
    reach INT,
    impressions INT,
    clicks INT
);

CREATE TABLE comments (
  comment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  post_id INT,
  user_id INT,
  comment_text TEXT,
  comment_date DATETIME
);

CREATE TABLE engagements (
  engagement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  post_id INT,
  user_id INT,
  engagement_type VARCHAR(10),
  engagement_date DATETIME
);
